                    <span data-lang="ja">ローカルツールキット。ブラウザ内で直接実行。Axiomのすべてのトレードから最大限の利益を引き出します。</span>
                </p>
                <a class="bookmarklet" href="#" data-style="inline-flex w-full justify-center items-center gap-2 bg-cta text-white font-display px-6 py-4 uppercase tracking-wider neon-cta border-2 border-cta">
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-lightning"></i>
                    <span><span data-lang="en">Установить</span><span data-lang="en">Install</span><span data-lang="zh">安装</span><span data-lang="es">Instalar</span><span data-lang="ja">インストール</span></span>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="neon-box p-8">
                <h2 class="font-display text-3xl uppercase text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                    <span data-lang="en">Радар Ликвидности</span>
                    <span data-lang="en">Liquidity Radar</span>
                    <span data-lang="zh">流动性雷达</span>
                    <span data-lang="es">Radar de Liquidez</span>
                    <span data-lang="ja">流動性レーダー</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6 border-l-2 border-accent pl-3">
                    <span data-lang="en">Анализ стакана в реальном времени.</span>
                    <span data-lang="en">Real-time order book analysis.</span>
                    <span data-lang="zh">实时订单簿分析。</span>
                    <span data-lang="es">Análisis del libro de órdenes en tiempo real.</span>
                    <span data-lang="ja">リアルタイムのオーダーブック分析。</span>
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-3 font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i class="ph-bold ph-check-square text-accent text-lg"></i> Anti-MEV Protection</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i class="ph-bold ph-check-square text-accent text-lg"></i> 100% Client-Side</li>
